data.description: Cross Creek subdivision. Close to the Golf Course! Wonderful three-bedroom, two full bath home on a Cul-de-sac. This home has a great layout. Walk in the front door and you will notice the high ceilings and the beautiful stone fireplace. The kitchen has a nice flow to the dining room, which leads to the newer patio. This outdoor space is great for entertaining. The shade trees are an added bonus. Upstairs you will two bedrooms with a jack and jill bathroom, new carpet on the second floor.  Great Storage in both garage and house attic. This home is a must see!!
